# Performance, Capacity, and Efficiency

Owner: Performance and Capacity Engineer.

Cover load, stress, spike, endurance, scalability, capacity, headroom, autoscaling, workload models, bottlenecks, resource requests/limits, performance budgets, and technical resource efficiency.

Use `.cursor/skills/performance-capacity-efficiency/SKILL.md` and `docs/performance-capacity-efficiency-workflows.md`.

Stop on requested benchmark/load-test execution, autoscaling or infrastructure mutation, production query, unverifiable performance claim, secret exposure, missing assumptions, or missing human approval.
